<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.6.7">
<l>poṟṟikaḻ cittira kūṭap poruppiṉi</l>
<l>luṟṟava ṭiviloru kaṇṇum koṇṭavak</l>
<l>kaṟṟaik kuḻalaṉ kaṭiyaṉ viraintuṉṉai</l>
<l>maṟṟaikkaṇ koḷḷāmē kōlkoṇṭuvā</l>
<l rend="indent">maṇivaṇṇa nampikkōr kōlkoṇṭuvā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bring a staff swiftly so that</l>
<l rend="indent">the cruel one, he with that knot of curly hair,</l>
<l rend="indent">who took one eye from the form that resided</l>
<l rend="indent">on Citrakūṭa mountain, which glitters of gold</l>
<l>doesn’t take your eye next.</l>
<l>Bring a staff for the sapphire hued prince.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
